                                                                                                Establish policy and authority            Planned         J. Doe       Do Now        XX/XX/XX
                                                                                                Establish and provide executive           Complete        …            Do Next       …
                                                                                                oversight and direction
                                                                                                Integrate C-SCRM into the enterprise      Delayed         …            Do Later      …
